      <title>索马里获得首个 5G，着眼于促进与该地区的贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/somalia-gets-first-5g-as-it-eyes-boosting-trade-with-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第一个第五代互联网服务已在索马里推出，旨在帮助促进这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家与其非洲邻国的贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/somalia-gets-first-5g-as-it-eyes-boosting-trade-with-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 16:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Reddit 首席运营官表示平台对于训练人工智能“极其重要”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/reddit-coo-says-platform-incredibly-important-for-training-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit Inc.首席运营官Jen Wong表示，该社交媒体网站将于周四开始公开交易，随着人工智能的发展，其数据许可业务将继续增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/reddit-coo-says-platform-incredibly-important-for-training-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 16:33:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在联合国集会支持在全球范围内协调“安全”人工智能系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/us-rallies-support-at-un-to-align-safe-ai-systems-globally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国大会批准了一项促进“安全、可靠和值得信赖”人工智能系统的决议，这是迄今为止为迅速崛起的颠覆性技术建立全球标准的最引人注目的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/us-rallies-support-at-un-to-align-safe-ai-systems-globally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 16:23:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果和谷歌将受到欧盟数字法的首次调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/apple-google-set-to-be-hit-by-first-probes-under-eu-digital-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司和 Alphabet 公司旗下的谷歌将面临欧盟的全面调查，调查它们是否遵守了一项限制大型科技公司权力的新法律，这为可能面临巨额罚款铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/apple-google-set-to-be-hit-by-first-probes-under-eu-digital-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:16:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街削减 IT 支出，埃森哲股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/accenture-slumps-as-wall-street-pulls-back-on-it-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃森哲公司下调了收入预期，并警告称，金融服务客户削减了在其软件上的支出，该公司股价出现四年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/accenture-slumps-as-wall-street-pulls-back-on-it-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就iPhone反垄断案起诉苹果公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/us-justice-department-sues-apple-in-antitrust-case-over-iphone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部和 16 名总检察长起诉苹果公司，指控这家 iPhone 制造商阻止竞争对手访问其热门设备上的硬件和软件功能，违反了反垄断法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/us-justice-department-sues-apple-in-antitrust-case-over-iphone</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:31:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佩尔茨得到 ISS 的支持，商界领袖参与迪士尼之战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/peltz-backed-to-improve-disney-by-group-of-business-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳尔逊·佩尔茨 (Nelson Peltz) 在加入娱乐公司华特迪士尼公司 (Walt Disney Co.) 董事会的过程中得到了一家有影响力的股东咨询公司和一群商界领袖的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/peltz-backed-to-improve-disney-by-group-of-business-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着与债权人的僵局加深，Altice France 向 Lazard 求助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/altice-france-creditors-are-working-on-a-debt-plan-with-houlihan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Altice France 及其债权人团体已开始与财务和法律顾问合作，该电信公司与其贷方之间就该公司债务负担的命运陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/altice-france-creditors-are-working-on-a-debt-plan-with-houlihan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 09:49:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 Neuralink 向患者展示了用意念控制视频游戏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/musk-s-neuralink-gives-update-on-first-brain-implant-patient</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 旗下的 Neuralink Corp. 周三直播了首例脑植入患者的最新情况，显示一名四肢瘫痪的男子能够用自己的思维玩视频游戏和在线国际象棋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/musk-s-neuralink-gives-update-on-first-brain-implant-patient</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 21:53:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
